Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我的眼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,直爽上进的决心太过耀眼
